{"tid":549101,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"鳥攝冰島","createTime":"2018-02-03T09:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T12:01:10.000Z","uid":56020,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b75105ed46998cfe4cca64ac31571aa092fdc61d","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"冰島風景好靚，不過唔講唔知其實冰島都好多雀仔睇。<br />\n<br />\n冰島係北極圈邊緣，會有北極圈先有嘅雀仔，例如北極燕鷗同海鸚。<br />\n而每到夏天(我就係夏去)就會有大量雀仔由南面遷移到冰島，所以係會見到香港冬天會見到嘅雀仔。<br />\n但有一點唔同嘅係你會係冰島見到佢地嘅BB，因為冰島係好多雀仔嘅繁殖地。<br />\n而另一樣同香港唔同嘅係----冰島雀唔係好驚人，好易影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身個trip唔係觀鳥trip，見到嘅雀有限(大約40種) ，所以唔會post太多品種。不過我會略略介紹某幾個觀鳥地點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一個地點係位於冰島首都Reykjav&iacute;k嘅Hlj&oacute;msk&aacute;lagar&eth;ur 公園<br />\n呢個園除左草地仲有個大湖，而湖入面有好多水鳥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4300/35784671741_e892989186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4300%2F35784671741_e892989186.jpg&h=4dd886a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港都算易見嘅紅嘴鷗<br />\n不過係冰島會係草地上見到，而且唔怕人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4310/35076687734_5cfa852b21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4310%2F35076687734_5cfa852b21.jpg&h=5c5a2836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳳頭潛鴨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4206/35528466800_8c199d9541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4206%2F35528466800_8c199d9541.jpg&h=73cd17c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去親高緯度地方就好易見到嘅綠頭鴨(雄)<br />\n呢隻男仔係到清理緊自己d毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4294/35784635171_8922754a7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4294%2F35784635171_8922754a7c.jpg&h=ab9162e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏灰銀鷗<br />\n香港都會見到，不過平時唔會咁近<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左呢幾款雀外，仲有天鵝同灰雁<br />\n係呢個地點可以見到好多冰島常見嘅城市雀，唔係好特別，不過係市中心，勝在方便。<br />\n如果唔方便去它又想睇雀，就可以去呢到hea下。<br />\n<br />\n-續-<br />\n<br />\n有興趣睇更多相歡迎follow IG 或 flickr<br />\n生態IG: gomenwl<br />\n建築/風景IG: gomenul<br />\nFlickr:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/gomensee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2Fgomensee%2F&d=BlW%2BZMQ4xO5zio%2BQKUV5mARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9ec6fb23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.flickr.com/photos/gomensee/</a>"},{"pid":"9f1e4ed249814bfbf0fea62f7ef0c68c6128c284","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"第二個想介紹嘅地方係冰島南部嘅冰河湖J&ouml;kuls&aacute;rl&oacute;n<br />\n冰河湖係好出名嘅景點，我係到等緊上觀光船嘅時候發現附近嘅草地其實有好大堆北極燕鷗!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4294/36026006885_e0ed6a91e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4294%2F36026006885_e0ed6a91e0.jpg&h=230586e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我去到嘅時候落緊雨，好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4474/37585246826_b246517d08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4474%2F37585246826_b246517d08.jpg&h=584cf7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到燕鷗記住唔好行太近，因為佢地會攻擊入侵者。<br />\n有個外國人行得太近，比佢地用雀屎攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地仲會圍毆人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係冰河湖附近散步嘅時候間唔中會見到燕鷗屍體，原來會有雀食燕鷗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警告: 圖片有d血腥</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4320/35854784552_6fe0e589f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4320%2F35854784552_6fe0e589f1.jpg&h=d77460a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賊鷗唔止會搶其它雀仔嘅食物，甚至會捕食其它雀仔。<br />\n係冰河湖到最少可以見到兩種賊鷗，上圖係大賊鷗，而另一款我見到嘅係短尾賊鷗，不過佢好遠，係浮冰上面，所以無相睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時候你會係停車場嘅小石地見到幾隻細雀仔<br />\n佢地係雪鵐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4308/35874534832_0c62096f84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4308%2F35874534832_0c62096f84.jpg&h=54004e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雪鵐係高維度先會有，適應寒冷氣候嘅小型雀仔，夏天嘅時候白色，而冬天嘅時候會變成啡紅色。<br />\n<br />\n冰河湖唔算好多雀仔睇不過就有好大堆北極燕鷗，而且好彩嘅話會見到海獅(雖然我影唔到&hellip;)<br />\n所以如果經過冰河湖，可以順便望下<br />\n<br />\n-續-"},{"pid":"285402b71675dd1888c5cc758711f29ce4c0bf02","tid":549101,"uid":79152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638857145875234e70405f2318faa3b9cb6fe7fe","tid":549101,"uid":7026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbad0ec5a18bfcaf44ba4c12914e8fe1d1056aa4","tid":549101,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3183d9eec61f288dc86c3a6ca8f56568f02b74e","tid":549101,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T19:58:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你副嘢個spec?"},{"pid":"92f15eaf8e4ff47c1456fe1c938c2ab3eff44163","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3183d9eec61f288dc86c3a6ca8f56568f02b74e","tid":549101,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T19:58:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你副嘢個spec?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"nikon d500 + 80-400mm"},{"pid":"e6b0fa8ef17157803677d76a90982eadfb5a81f7","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285402b71675dd1888c5cc758711f29ce4c0bf02","tid":549101,"uid":79152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:18:46.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2beb1e15f6c622c1da0032ead36bcfd5e3e96a","tid":549101,"uid":117044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"509574142bf58497223681b6ff3205880bc4240d","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"米湖(M&yacute;vatn)可以話係今個trip最多雀仔睇嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n米湖係冰島北部，係2000幾年之前火山爆完之後變成嘅淡水湖。<br />\n呢到出名夏天多水鳥<br />\n其中一個原因令到米湖咁多雀係因為米湖好多蟲(呢種蟲冰島話係M&yacute;, 英文係midge) ，不過好彩佢地唔多咬人。<br />\n<br />\n米湖有勁多紅領瓣足鷸，隻隻都係到不斷捉蟲食唔唔多理人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4441/36349472455_58b8314222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4441%2F36349472455_58b8314222.jpg&h=955987c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻男仔掛住捉蟲，完全無視我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4311/36309033965_09b09cea81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4311%2F36309033965_09b09cea81.jpg&h=b5781799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻靚女好乖，仲識望鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4316/36141932132_6bca38a956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4316%2F36141932132_6bca38a956.jpg&h=e661b7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港無乜可能見到嘅針尾鴨BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽媽帶住佢地過馬路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4639/39147454692_bd38e57b91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4639%2F39147454692_bd38e57b91.jpg&h=f20a10b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來佢地食草的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4387/36180625442_c909f8c79c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4387%2F36180625442_c909f8c79c.jpg&h=5fd9108a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有好靚嘅角鸊鷉<br />\n<br />\n米湖當然唔止呢d雀，不過我就唔夠時間睇多d雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趕住走<br />\n<br />\n-續-"},{"pid":"980d690aa7b6c6b17a5f89ff054747e314fb490a","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"鳥攝冰島定冰島攝鳥呀"},{"pid":"76182d11d444c3957df976d3ff77dfe6d82a1799","tid":549101,"uid":44082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05e7d67497fe1fb67d04fc79ce4f8ad01c84ffa","tid":549101,"uid":139505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳥攝冰島定冰島攝鳥呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以為航拍"},{"pid":"d640f05f8f1a98daa8c55a547ae31661f88b25fe","tid":549101,"uid":17619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"980d690aa7b6c6b17a5f89ff054747e314fb490a","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"鳥攝冰島定冰島攝鳥呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"冰島。鳥攝"},{"pid":"b59eba342a5456f46f6e7da95c16cfaaa2cf13c4","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"980d690aa7b6c6b17a5f89ff054747e314fb490a","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"鳥攝冰島定冰島攝鳥呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"咁下次寫冰島影雀算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68406b3ea04a1aeeebbae8b555749f568d9f1cc9","tid":549101,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"師兄唔錯"},{"pid":"bdde00978318b8d31bf96b1c4c04c7217ad01020","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"H&uacute;sav&iacute;k係冰島北面嘅鎮，<br />\n呢到唔係一個睇雀聖地，不過就係一個觀鯨聖地<br />\n係呢到坐船去睇鯨魚會有&gt;90%機會見到座頭鯨<br />\n<br />\n我地見到兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/215204_e34491d0e2f0b3230d52e65d5488d7e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F215204_e34491d0e2f0b3230d52e65d5488d7e9.jpg&h=4d368399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/215216_b0fd210809ea00e27fde772aa341f168.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F215216_b0fd210809ea00e27fde772aa341f168.jpg&h=b225db07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左鯨魚，海上面仲會有唔少背極圈先有嘅雀<br />\n例如有暴雪鸌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4408/35730523424_60f3a71b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4408%2F35730523424_60f3a71b17.jpg&h=4e5bee16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冰島國鳥 北極海鸚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4395/36519004386_14aff98300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4395%2F36519004386_14aff98300.jpg&h=9f44eed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有d島可以坐船上去睇海鸚，不過我呢個團唔包 :(<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個海上面當然唔止呢兩種雀，不過佢地一係太遠一係飛得太快影唔到<br />\n所以去呢到都係望下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-續-"},{"pid":"e9deb1096428d20ce65a1a477990ae21cef3e240","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59eba342a5456f46f6e7da95c16cfaaa2cf13c4","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"980d690aa7b6c6b17a5f89ff054747e314fb490a","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"鳥攝冰島定冰島攝鳥呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"咁下次寫冰島影雀算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"影出面隻雀定佢自已隻雀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844b8bbe3939090e559eae8d0b6fd5593c76e1ba","tid":549101,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61df2ae584d3417457b21b912c547d87d2d85666","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"844b8bbe3939090e559eae8d0b6fd5593c76e1ba","tid":549101,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9deb1096428d20ce65a1a477990ae21cef3e240","tid":549101,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59eba342a5456f46f6e7da95c16cfaaa2cf13c4","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"咁下次寫冰島影雀算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"影出面隻雀定佢自已隻雀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"結冰雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdf64a7f20c77dbe5cd967adec3d2b319752c0e","tid":549101,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:19:31.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n期待"},{"pid":"168e21dd7d5c6d410dc0f3ace06ca125c5d8be06","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"後記<br />\n<br />\n跟住落黎介紹嘅地方實唔係乜野特別觀鳥地點，只係酒店附近嘅草地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個時朝早食完早餐就係酒店附近行個圈就見到雀<br />\n<br />\n我係Sk&oacute;gar嘅酒店附近遇到蠣鴴爸爸、媽媽同BB，<br />\n不過佢地明顯有戒心，唔易靠近<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4292/35892323071_e92297fbcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4292%2F35892323071_e92297fbcb.jpg&h=e9ae8039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4320/36003713996_f8f650c3e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4320%2F36003713996_f8f650c3e4.jpg&h=003d8c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4736/38467026834_cbec9b54b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4736%2F38467026834_cbec9b54b3.jpg&h=3d5b3a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而係Sn&aelig;fellsnes半島嘅酒店嘅草地就遇到中杓鷸<br />\n第一張係日落影，第二張係朝早影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4406/35533926474_e53dc96b2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4406%2F35533926474_e53dc96b2d.jpg&h=f2b7255e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4713/26526399478_eac1d829df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4713%2F26526399478_eac1d829df.jpg&h=91064432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有幾隻BB，不過有d遠，影得差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當大家見到BB雀嘅時候要特別小心，<br />\n因為帶住bb嘅成鳥都會特別有攻擊性，<br />\n如果太急接近d雀，佢地係會攻擊你<br />\n我見過有人行得太近，d雀痾屎落佢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果對動物有興趣，歡迎follow IG:<br />\n<br />\ngomenwl<br />\n<br />\n或者對風景、建築有興趣可以follow另一個 account:<br />\n<br />\ngomenul<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝各位支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有乜野想知無論關於個trip定係雀都歡迎隨便討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-完-"},{"pid":"09115b0c751798e21f6dfdb367c9b0e5f0f55402","tid":549101,"uid":175187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"亂入幾張喺Faroe Islands影嘅海鸚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/w3s0d4h53/P8070369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fw3s0d4h53%2FP8070369.jpg&h=069eb4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/k1wmizfmf/P8070412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fk1wmizfmf%2FP8070412.jpg&h=3796140f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/4gfaz1bdz/P8070425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2F4gfaz1bdz%2FP8070425.jpg&h=3784b359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/swxgtijuf/P8070484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fswxgtijuf%2FP8070484.jpg&h=2bd51bc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e48ba7440668e92fb5a53e50525c4d5a467e2d2","tid":549101,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"交通、機票果啲點<br />\n想了解下"},{"pid":"d39e1cab85f5bdff7e502749d41800e557b378ab","tid":549101,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e48ba7440668e92fb5a53e50525c4d5a467e2d2","tid":549101,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"交通、機票果啲點<br />\n想了解下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"我跟團去<br />\n機票萬幾蚊，坐旅遊巴<br />\n<br />\n如果你自己去想環島最好自駕遊<br />\n如果只係玩南面都可以參加d local short tour，佢地有d會有車接送"}]}